How to Play!
The rules of the game are simple, Guess all the letters in a word!
Every completely guessed word fetches the player 10 points!
But in order to make this a lot more challenging, a few constraints have been included.
Every player has 10 lives and the game ends when you lose all your lives.
You lose a life whenever you make an incorrect guess.
Click the "HINT" button to get a description of the Word you are to guess.
But BEWARE! Getting a hint for a word deducts 5 points from your score!
Now that you know how to play, Let the Games Begin!